{"title":"这个季节","authors":["彭国梁"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":10,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彭国梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都忍耐了这么久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待了这么久"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到下雨的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随便唱支什么歌吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“走过春天  走过我自己”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦跨过了自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生会轻松得多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也潇洒得多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然这个季节的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放了又将凋谢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然这个季节的幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"降临后不免带来痛苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要有人还需要爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串一串的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会不停地荡漾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天，永远不会老去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了这个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不该总把脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸进过去的某一天里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缅怀曾有过的欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不该再寻问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面是否有醉人的时光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了这个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就该相信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有许多洒满阳光的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经在远方召唤"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}